    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## Use AI as a Data Visualization Coach\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to interpret different data visualizations.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nDo This:\r\n1. Upload the **data visualization** from the library by selecting **+ Add file > From Library**.\r\n2. Ask AI Chat one of these questions:\r\n    - *Here's my chart. What trends or patterns might I be missing?*\r\n    - *What kind of question could I answer with this chart?*\r\n    - *How would you describe this bar graph to someone who can't see it?*\r\n    - *How could this data visualization be misleading to someone?*",
